$DEF_BOITE
Gosub HORODAT From WGIMBIC
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Inpbox "IMBIC" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [MTB3]
& As [MTB3]
Titled [MTB3] TIT
Return

$VISU_BOITE
Gosub INIT_BOITE
Gosub HORODAT From WGIMBIC
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Inpbox "IMBIC" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [MTB3]
& As [MTB3]
Titled [MTB3] TIT
Gosub AFF_BOITE
Return

